OL,3,CInfected blood victim says inquiry's
OL,4,Cfindings 'nothing we didn't know'
OL,6,FA man infected with contaminated blood
OL,7,Fwhile receiving treatment for
OL,8,Fleukaemia has said the damning
OL,9,Ffindings of an inquiry into the
OL,10,Fscandal are "nothing we didn't know
OL,11,Falready".
OL,13,FStuart Hall, from Workington, cwhich
OL,14,Fleft him with severe health problems,
OL,15,Fincluding cirrhosis and liver cancer,
OL,16,Ffor which he needed a transplant in
OL,17,F2021.
