OL,6,FMr Hall required regular ultrasounds
OL,7,Fto check for cancerous lesions every
OL,8,Fsix months after his hepatitis
OL,9,Fdiagnosis, which he said had "taken
OL,10,Ffrom me what people would consider a
OL,11,Fnormal life, without the constant
OL,12,Fworry of a condition that, ultimately,
OL,13,Fyou could die from".
OL,15,FWhat did the inquiry find?
OL,17,FThe inquiry today found there were a
OL,18,Fcatalogue of failures which led to a
OL,19,F"treatment disaster" that could
OL,20,Flargely have been avoided - and should
OL,21,Fhave been.
