OL,3,CInfected blood victim says inquiry's
OL,4,Cfindings 'nothing we didn't know'
OL,6,FHe said: "The government is right to
OL,7,Faccept that compensation must be paid.
OL,8,FNow is the time for national
OL,9,Frecognition of this disaster and for
OL,10,Fproper compensation to all who have
OL,11,Fbeen wronged."
OL,13,FMr Hall told ITV Border the report's
OL,14,Ffindings were "known about long, long
OL,15,Fago", adding: "There was a high chance
OL,16,Fthat blood donations would be infected
OL,17,Fwith a virus (in the 1970s and 1980s)."
