OL,3,CInfected blood victim says inquiry's
OL,4,Cfindings 'nothing we didn't know'
OL,6,FHe said the last 30 years have had "a
OL,7,Fhuge mental toll" on him and his wife,
OL,8,FJulie, who has supported him through
OL,9,Fevery ultrasound, cancer scare, and
OL,10,Feventually his liver transplant.
OL,12,FHe said: "You shouldn't be spending 30
OL,13,Fyears worrying that you may die from
OL,14,Fsomething that you know is attacking
OL,15,Fyour liver.
OL,17,F"I was very lucky to clear the virus
OL,18,Feventually in 2012. I had a 48 weeks
OL,19,Fcourse of an antiviral and a course of
OL,20,Fchemotherapy treatment which cleared
OL,21,Fthe virus.
