OL,6,F"But unfortunately by then the liver
OL,7,Fwas cirrhotic and damaged beyond
OL,8,Frepair."
OL,10,FMr Hall said he is now waiting to see
OL,11,Fwhether prosecutions can come from the
OL,12,Ffindings of the report.
OL,14,FWill infected blood scandal victims
OL,15,Fget compensation?
OL,17,FThe government is now working at pace
OL,18,Fto get a compensation body set up,
OL,19,Fhaving faced criticism in the past
OL,20,Fover the speed at which it responded
OL,21,Fto calls for action on compensation.
