OL,6,FInterim compensation payments of
OL,7,F#100,000 have been made to around
OL,8,F4,000 infected people or bereaved
OL,9,Fpartners, following advice from the
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,FMinisters recently announced that
OL,13,Fthese interim payments would be
OL,14,Fextended to the "estates of the
OL,15,Fdeceased".
OL,17,FIn April 2023, Sir Brian said interim
OL,18,Fcompensation should also be offered to
OL,19,Fthe children and parents of those
OL,20,Finfected.
